      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. IRINKA FRED filled a minor placing last start at Temora behind My Rupee (19.07) in a Grade 5. Has never missed the frame from four starts from this draw, including a win. Rates highly and will give a great sight. 2. LET'S GO JUDE has missed the frame at her last couple of starts but just a few runs back broke the clock when winning over 318m at Dubbo, taking a Grade 3/4 in a superb 18.16. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. 1. DIG DEEP RUPEE turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.36) at this track behind Reggae Ethics in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to be in the finish again. 8. SUNNY SUE can sneak into the finish.\",\"runners\":[7,2,1,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
